---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Partner Venues - Sports Digital Network"
  description="Partner with SDN to create new revenue streams for your arena, recreation facility, or golf course with premium digital advertising displays."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Partner With SDN</h1>
    <p>Create new revenue streams while enhancing the experience for your community</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 1000px;">
      <div class="intro-box">
        <h2>More Than a Revenue Stream</h2>
        <p>Your facility is already a community hub. Families gather here. Friendships form here. Memories are made here.</p>
        <p>Partnering with SDN means bringing premium digital displays to your venue—creating new revenue while keeping your facility looking modern and professional. Our screens showcase relevant, community-appropriate content that enhances the atmosphere, not distracts from it.</p>
        <p><strong>We handle everything:</strong> installation, maintenance, content management, and advertiser relationships. You focus on running your facility. We focus on generating revenue.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="values" style="background: var(--cream);">
    <div class="values-container" style="max-width: 1200px;">
      <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: center;">Why Venues Choose SDN</h2>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128176;</div>
          <h3>Guaranteed Revenue</h3>
          <p>Predictable monthly income with no effort required. We manage all sales, content, and advertiser relationships.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#127912;</div>
          <h3>Premium Equipment</h3>
          <p>State-of-the-art displays installed and maintained at no cost to you. We keep your facility looking cutting-edge.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128737;</div>
          <h3>Content Control</h3>
          <p>Final approval on all advertising. We ensure every ad aligns with your facility's values and community standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128250;</div>
          <h3>Community Content</h3>
          <p>Showcase schedules, scores, announcements, and sponsor recognition alongside paid advertising.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128295;</div>
          <h3>Zero Maintenance</h3>
          <p>We handle all technical support, updates, and repairs. Your staff has nothing to manage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit">
          <div class="benefit-icon">&#128200;</div>
          <h3>Growing Partnership</h3>
          <p>As our network expands, so does advertiser interest—meaning increasing revenue potential over time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Let's Explore Partnership</h2>
    <p>See how SDN can create value for your facility and community</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-white">Start a Conversation</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
